{"tid":753433,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)超人特工隊 神秘電影","createTime":"2018-07-23T15:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T18:20:43.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"df5e24bc823e493735c970899ecda98120ba6a75","tid":753433,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:02:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=ZRRphKpkSfPSlxEcrJivEAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=44367bf7\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=ZRRphKpkSfPSlxEcrJivEAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d209366e\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=ZRRphKpkSfPSlxEcrJivEAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=bf322df3\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e0/Tiposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe0%2FTiposter.jpg&h=1e960626&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/27/The_Incredibles_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F27%2FThe_Incredibles_2.jpg&h=8cce55ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.在一個生活著眾多超級英雄的社會，所有超級英雄在打擊犯罪的時候，也給周遭市民造成眾多災難與負擔。當市民們開始猛烈地對超級英雄們表示譴責和法律訴訟時，政府為平息事件只能實施《超級英雄異地安置計劃》為他們建造新的身份、住所與工作，而超級英雄也從此銷聲匿跡。十五年後，當年力大無窮被稱為「超能先生」的巴鮑伯，和跟身為「彈力女超人」的巴荷莉戀愛結婚後，共同育有三個子女：巴小倩（Violet）、巴小飛（Dash）和巴小傑（Jack-Jack）；他們也都各自遺傳到不同的超能力，也在父母的要求下盡力隱瞞。如今生活平凡、處於中年危機的鮑伯當起保險公司理賠員，一心只想著能繼續行俠仗義，並和多年的戰友「酷冰俠」（Frozone）夜晚時偷偷地在外救人<br />\n<br />\n2.在擊潰辛拉登後的三個月，超能一家在路上遇到「採礦大師」的襲擊。但是他們沒能逮到他，還破壞了城市。因此他們被警方約談，被迫放棄此工作，並暫時住在狄瑞克想盡辦法借來的汽車旅館，但只有兩個星期。要是他們沒能找到工作，就只能流浪街頭。企業總裁戴文森正在招募超級英雄希望讓其合法化<br />\n<br />\n11 20PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2係薯片版<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=ZRRphKpkSfPSlxEcrJivEAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=a1e736fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=ZRRphKpkSfPSlxEcrJivEAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=17de4c46\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42708ce398a6952bb029ebda3d157f453313d12b","tid":753433,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebe26b1b572d37e0427ff4e819da16c21855ea2","tid":753433,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:29:10.000Z","